quote.p:
Group 1, subdivision 1. Of the foregoing commodities you request
                                    the following increases: 

Coffee to 16,000 tons;

Tea to 600 tons;

Spices to 500 tons;

Pepper to 168 tons;

Rubber, rubber goods, rubber shoes and rubber tires to
                                            500 tons. This quantity to be increased to 700 tons,
                                            provided Denmark can prove her real need of this
                                            quantity.
